message.entry: Invalid State Validator. State validator for stateSpaceSE3 must be validatorOccupancyMap3D.
Invalid State Validator. State validator for stateSpaceSE2, stateSpaceDubins or stateSpaceReedsShepp must be validatorOccupancyMap or validatorVehicleCostmap.
Unable to use occupancy map due to insufficient memory. Reduce the dimensions or the Resolution property of the occupancy map.
